4.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ahh1714477179574.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ahh1714477179574.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bzy1665702782893\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $ltrim\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bzy1665702782893___ltrim_274593\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Trim the left side of a string from the left, following a pattern.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__topic_d85949e1_d85950e1_d85951e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__p_d85952e1_d85953e1_d85954e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ltrim</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Pattern</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__section_w4123ab1b7b5_w4124ab1b7_w4125ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__p_d85955e1_d85956e1_d85957e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vString = $ltrim(\"xxxxUniface\",\"x\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__topic_d57137e1_d57138e1_d57139e1_d57140e1_d57141e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334401e91\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__3\">\n String to be left trimmed.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Pattern</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bzy1665702782893__table_d9083e1_d9084e1_d9085e1__entry__3\"> Pattern to remove. It can be a constant\n                        string, regex string, or syntax string. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eiq1665702555322.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eiq1665702555322.html\" title=\"Uniface enables you to determine if the data in a string value matches a desired pattern using syntax strings. A syntax string is a group of characters and syntax codes (#, *, &amp;, @, ~, ?, (, ), %, and ^) enclosed in single quotation marks (').\">Syntax Strings for Pattern Matching</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1714308484693.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1714308484693.html\" title=\"Uniface enables you to determine if the data in a string value matches a desired pattern using regex strings. A regex string is a regular expression enclosed in forward slashes (‘/’).\">Regex Strings for Pattern Matching</a>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__topic_d57142e1_d57143e1_d57144e1_d57145e1_d57146e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334401e211\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__d6361e20\">Trimmed string.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__topic_d57147e1_d57148e1_d57149e1_d57150e1_d57151e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334401e221\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__p_d85970e1_d85971e1_d85972e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__section_nnc_jwb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d334401e230\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ltrim</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ahh1714477179574_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__codeblock_b5j_v12_gbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vString1=\"xxxxUniface\"\nvString2 = $ltrim(vString1,\"x\")\n; vString2 now contains \"Uniface\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bzy1665702782893__pre_pzn_jwb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vString = $ltrim(\"xxxxUnifacexxxx\",$regex(\"x\"))\n; vString now is \"Unifacexxxx\"\nvString = $ltrim(\"xxxx\",$regex(\"x\"))\n; vString now is \"\"vString = $ltrim(\"1111234567890111uniface\",$regex(\"\\d\"))\n; vString now is \"uniface\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ogn1714481964573.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$rtrim</a><p>Trim a string on the right-hand side, following a pattern.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6809883\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6809883\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$ltrim Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $ltrim Trim the left side of a string from the left, following a pattern. $ltrim ( Source , Pattern ) Example: vString = $ltrim(\"xxxxUniface\",\"x\") Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Source String String to be left trimmed. Pattern String Pattern to remove. It can be a constant string, regex string, or syntax string. For more information, see Syntax Strings for Pattern Matching and Regex Strings for Pattern Matching . Return Values Trimmed string. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $ltrim Explain this code vString1=\"xxxxUniface\" vString2 = $ltrim(vString1,\"x\") ; vString2 now contains \"Uniface\" Copy vString = $ltrim(\"xxxxUnifacexxxx\",$regex(\"x\")) ; vString now is \"Unifacexxxx\" vString = $ltrim(\"xxxx\",$regex(\"x\")) ; vString now is \"\"vString = $ltrim(\"1111234567890111uniface\",$regex(\"\\d\")) ; vString now is \"uniface\" Copy Related Links $rtrim Trim a string on the right-hand side, following a pattern. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}